ion or termination of the Regulatory Agreement, or (iii) the date upon which the Exemption Area ceases to be owned by either a housing development fund company or an entity wholly controlled by a housing development fund company.\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\fi-360\\li360\\par\n\\pard\\cbpat2\\ltrpar\\fi-4320\\li5910\\qj\\cf1 Office of the City Clerk,     \\}                                                               \\par\n\\pard\\cbpat2\\ltrpar\\li1590\\qj The City of New York        \\} ss.:\\par\n\\pard\\cbpat2\\ltrpar\\qj  \\par\nI hereby certify that the foregoing is a true copy of a Resolution passed by The Council of the City of New York on May 23, 2018, on file in this office.\\par\n\\pard\\cbpat2\\ltrpar\\fi5040\\qj  \\par\n_______________________\\par\nCity Clerk, Clerk of Council\\par\n}\n",
